dataset.prop: CDNA was prepared from polyA+ RNA using the SMART cDNA Library Construction Kit and was cloned into the pOTB7b vector, a derivative of pOTB7 (1.8 kb) in which a SfiI stuffer fragment was inserted between the BamHI and XhoI sites of pOTB7.PFOCB48 indicates plate and well. T indicates dye terminator chemistry. F and R indicates M13 forward and reverse primers.The R primer is at the 3' polyA end of the mRNA.
